1.	Where do you want to be in five years? open ended, can help to show ambition, tough to do well. If you do it well, looks really good
2.	Tell me about a time you worked with a difficult person.
3.	Describe your experience working in a team.
4.	(I got this question in an actual interview) Have you worked in a service industry?
5.	How do you deal with fast paced environments? What speed do you prefer?
6.	Tell me about a time you showed leadership
7.	Of which three accomplishments are you most proud?
8.	Why did you choose us?
9.	What a weakness that you have? 
10.	What skills or ideas do you bring to a job that another candidate may not be able to offer?
